A bustling workshop scene in Bangkok rendered in Studio Ghibli style, showing a warm sunlit room filled with enthusiastic developers gathered around laptops, their faces glowing with excitement and discovery. Golden afternoon light streams through tall windows draped with flowing curtains, casting soft shadows across wooden desks cluttered with notebooks and coffee cups. In the foreground, a young developer leans forward intently, eyes wide with an "aha moment" as colorful interface elements seem to float magically above their screen like gentle spirits. The background shows the distinctive silhouette of Bangkok temples through the windows, with soft clouds drifting in a pastel sky. The atmosphere radiates collaborative energy and creative breakthrough, with subtle warm oranges and cool blues creating visual harmony throughout the composition.
